{"word":"ὁμοιόω","slug":"ὁμοιόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὁμοιόω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὅμοιος\">ὅμοιος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘cause to be like’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> sense <b>be like, become like <a href='B:470 6:8'>Mt 6:8</a>; <a href='B:470 7:24'>7:24</a>, <a href='B:470 7:26'>26</a>; <a href='B:510 14:11'>Ac 14:11</a>; <a href='B:520 9:29'>Ro 9:29</a>; <a href='B:650 2:17'>Hb 2:17</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘make a comparison’, <b>compare <a href='B:470 7:24'>Mt 7:24</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:470 11:16'>11:16</a>; <a href='B:480 4:30'>Mk 4:30</a>; <a href='B:490 13:18'>Lk 13:18</a>, <a href='B:490 13:20'>20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὁμοιότης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὁμοίωμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}